+
+## 6. Phases
+
+### Phase 0 — Complete ✓
+Engine implementation and iris gold regression.
+- Binary ODA engine proven faithful
+- Multiclass ODA engine proven faithful (two-level SAMPLEREP)
+- ODA LOO proven faithful (true refit-per-fold)
